<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="General:_scholarly_secondary_sources">General: scholarly secondary sources</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=History_of_American_newspapers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=42" title="Edit section: General: scholarly secondary sources"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
