<li>Daly, Chris. "The Historiography of Journalism History: Part 1:'An Overview.'." <i>American Journalism</i> 26 (2009): 141–147; "The Historiography of Journalism History: Part 2: 'Toward a New Theory,'" <i>American Journalism</i> (2009) 26#1 pp 148–155, stresses the tension between the imperative form of business model and the dominating culture of news</li>
<li>Hampton, Mark, and Martin Conboy. "Journalism history—a debate." <i>Journalism Studies</i> (2014) 15#2 (2014) pp: 154–171. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/1461670X.2013.816547#.VC2jXhaOpu0">online</a></li>
